				<td colspan="2"><span>I had a friend who played a shaman alt.   We would play together a ton.   This worked will for us all the way up to our low 50's.  He would have his pet.  I would pull with a chant and he would slow.  
<br />

<br />
4 chants on the mob would hold aggro pretty well.  Even if he has to slow more then once because of resist  (I am not sure with the new aggro changes if this will work)
<br />

<br />
I would play mana/hp regen during down time.    
<br />

<br />
We did 6 pop inculding the named at that camp as a duo.    We where not twinked really and just on par gear at the time.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
