Basicly pull with bard, and debuff + slow on inc, melee it while he heals me till its at around 90%, he uses his slow. I can usually keep agro, but if it goes to him, he just takes the beating. His gear is nice for his level so its not a big deal. Once the mob is at around 60%, he can drop a DoT or two, and I can still keep agro if things have been going well.
<br />

